<p><b>  Report on the seminar: &#8220;A human rights approach to 
combating human trafficking: challenges and opportunities. 
Implementing the Recommended Principles and Guidelines 
on Human Rights and Human Trafficking&#8221;  
(Geneva, 27 and 28 May 2010)</b>*<b> 
